Robot Arm State
===============================================================================

The robot arm state context exposes mock state from the demo host.

1. Context
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```text
arm/state
```

2. Read paths
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

| Path | Description |
|------|-------------|
| `position` | Last mock position value. |
| `gripper` | Last mock gripper value. |
| `last-command` | Last command name accepted by the host. |

3. Example
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

```mech
+> @state := arm/state

position := @state/position
last-command := @state/last-command
```

State paths are read-only.
